snippet.title: Champions of Krynn
snippet.description:
Champions of Krynn, a classic computer RPG that's part of the Gold Box collection.

Here's more info:
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Champions_of_Krynn

Also, the art on the cover of the box:
http://i31.tinypic.com/11ju7og.jpg

And the ad for the game:
http://i25.tinypic.com/331oyg1.jpg
